    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it just feels like there's nothing left to give. everything is so hard now, even just getting out of bed. my kids... they're so busy and stressed, and here I am just another thing they have to worry about every single day. i hate seeing that look in their eyes when they come over. i feel like i'm just a burden to them at this point.",
